  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Like the waves coming to the beach,</l>
            <l>So does our time <choice><orig>comes</orig><reg>come</reg></choice> to an end,</l>
            <l>Every changing place at which we were,</l>
            <l>Stand all up for the final fight.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>At the beginning there was the birth,</l>
            <l>And after growing up you can get the crown,</l>
            <l>Cringed eclipses against his fight,</l>
            <l>And time that fave has now <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="word">contounded</gap> his gift.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Time kills the best tie set on youth,</l>
            <l>And searching for parallels in beauty's face;</l>
            <l>Full with the rarities of nature's truth,</l>
            <l>And there is nothing but his mower</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>And this sonnet shall stand in times of hope,</l>
            <l>Praising your worth, despite his cruel hand.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
